## Modules and Workspaces

101. Basic of Terraform Modules 
-----✌️✌️✌️✌️🖖🫳🫴👌🤘🤟------
DRY principle = Do not repeat yourself 
With Terraform modules, multiple team can create standardized modules for other teams to reuse. This helps the team for not having to write the code from the scratch. 
Its a very popular way to consume Terraform, which is available on the Terraform official site. 


102. Creating EC2 instances using modules 
-----✌️✌️✌️✌️🖖🫳🫴👌🤘🤟------

Go to the official site, and read the Provisions instructions. Copy the code and create a new file. 
Once the terraform init command is created, the module will be downloaded. 
Sample code snippet from ec2-instance: ec2-module.tf 
module "ec2-instance"  {
source = "terraform-ec2-module/ec2-instance/aws"
version = "5.6.1.7"
  }

